<exercise checkit-seed="0034" checkit-slug="E1" checkit-title="Linear systems, vector equations, and augmented matrices">
  <statement>
    <p> Consider the system of equations
            <md alignment="alignat" alignat-columns=" 4 "><mrow>x_{1} &amp;+&amp; 2 \, x_{2} &amp;-&amp; 5 \, x_{3} &amp;=&amp; -8</mrow><mrow>-x_{1} &amp;-&amp; x_{2} &amp;+&amp; x_{3} &amp;=&amp; 1</mrow><mrow> &amp; &amp;  &amp; &amp; x_{3} &amp;=&amp; 2</mrow><mrow> &amp; &amp; x_{2} &amp;-&amp; 4 \, x_{3} &amp;=&amp; -7</mrow></md></p>
    <ol>
      <li> Write an augmented matrix corresponding to this system. </li>
      <li> Write a vector equation corresponding to this system. </li>
    </ol>
  </statement>
  <answer>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <me> \left[\begin{array}{ccc|c}
1 &amp; 2 &amp; -5 &amp; -8 \\
-1 &amp; -1 &amp; 1 &amp; 1 \\
0 &amp; 0 &amp; 1 &amp; 2 \\
0 &amp; 1 &amp; -4 &amp; -7
\end{array}\right] </me>
      </li>
      <li>
        <me> x_{1} \left[\begin{array}{c}
1 \\
-1 \\
0 \\
0
\end{array}\right] + x_{2} \left[\begin{array}{c}
2 \\
-1 \\
0 \\
1
\end{array}\right] + x_{3} \left[\begin{array}{c}
-5 \\
1 \\
1 \\
-4
\end{array}\right] = \left[\begin{array}{c}
-8 \\
1 \\
2 \\
-7
\end{array}\right] </me>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </answer>
</exercise>

